Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Convenient, Mixed-Use Building, Centrally Located in the East End

Offices at Baum houses 60,000 SF of contemporary office space, supported by ground floor retail amenities, as well as an integral parking garage. 

Tenants enjoy quick grab-and-go grocery shopping at the recently remodeled ALDI, and have immediate access to a premium coffee shop at Crazy Mocha, both on-site.
